       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CONTRACT-AWARD-ADJUDICATION.

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-ZSERIES.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-ZSERIES.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-DECISION                  PIC X(7) VALUE "REVIEW ".
       01  WS-REASON                    PIC X(80) VALUE SPACES.
       01  WS-CONTRACT-STATUS           PIC X(8) VALUE SPACES.
       01  WS-OBLIGATED-AMOUNT          PIC 9(10) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-VENDOR-ACTIVE-COUNT       PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-VENDOR-TOTAL-AWARDS       PIC 9(12) VALUE ZERO.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-LOGIC.
           IF WS-CONTRACT-STATUS NOT = "ACTIVE"
               MOVE "REJECT " TO WS-DECISION
               MOVE "CONTRACT STATUS NOT ACTIVE" TO WS-REASON
               GO TO PROGRAM-END
           END-IF

           IF WS-OBLIGATED-AMOUNT < 1000000
               MOVE "REJECT " TO WS-DECISION
               MOVE "OBLIGATED AMOUNT BELOW THRESHOLD" TO WS-REASON
               GO TO PROGRAM-END
           END-IF

           IF WS-OBLIGATED-AMOUNT >= 120000000
               MOVE "REVIEW " TO WS-DECISION
               MOVE "HIGH DOLLAR AWARD REQUIRES REVIEW" TO WS-REASON
               GO TO PROGRAM-END
           END-IF

           IF WS-VENDOR-ACTIVE-COUNT >= 5
               MOVE "REVIEW " TO WS-DECISION
               MOVE "VENDOR WORKLOAD CONCENTRATION" TO WS-REASON
               GO TO PROGRAM-END
           END-IF

           IF WS-VENDOR-TOTAL-AWARDS >= 500000000
               MOVE "REVIEW " TO WS-DECISION
               MOVE "CUMULATIVE AWARD WATCH THRESHOLD" TO WS-REASON
               GO TO PROGRAM-END
           END-IF

           MOVE "APPROVE" TO WS-DECISION
           MOVE "ALL AUTOMATED CHECKS PASSED" TO WS-REASON.

       PROGRAM-END.
           GOBACK.
